{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id788d65b1-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s742h"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"742h"},"text":"§ 742h.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Reports on fishery products","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id788d65b2-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s742h/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Repealed. ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/470/tI/s103/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–470, title I, § 103(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1980-10-19"},"text":"Oct. 19, 1980","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/94/2237"},"text":"94 Stat. 2237","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id788d65b3-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s742h/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" The Secretary is authorized to make a report to the President and the Congress, and, when requested by the United States International Trade Commission in connection with ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t19/s1364"},"text":"section 1364 of title 19","children":[],"tail":", or when an investigation is made under the Tariff Act of 1930 ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t19/s1332"},"text":"19 U.S.C. 1332","children":[],"tail":"), the Secretary is authorized to make a report to such Commission, concerning the following matters with respect to any fishery product which is imported into the United States, or such reports may be made upon a request from any segment of the domestic industry producing a like or directly competitive product—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id788d65b4-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s742h/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" whether there has been a downward trend in the production, employment in the production, or prices, or a decline in the sales, of the like or directly competitive product by the domestic industry; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id788d65b5-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s742h/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" whether there has been an increase in the imports of the fishery products into the United States, either actual or relative to the production of the like or directly competitive product produced by the domestic industry.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id788d65b6-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1956-08-08/ch1036/s9"},"text":"Aug. 8, 1956, ch. 1036, § 9","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/70/1123"},"text":"70 Stat. 1123","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/93/618/tI/s171/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 93–618, title I, § 171(b)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1975-01-03"},"text":"Jan. 3, 1975","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/88/2009"},"text":"88 Stat. 2009","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/470/tI/s103/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–470, title I, § 103(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1980-10-19"},"text":"Oct. 19, 1980","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/94/2237"},"text":"94 Stat. 2237","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id788d65b7-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id788d65b8-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id788d65b9-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t19/s1364"},"text":"Section 1364 of title 19","children":[],"tail":", referred to in subsec. (b), was repealed by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/87/794/tII/s257/e/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 87–794, title II, § 257(e)(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1962-10-11"},"text":"Oct. 11, 1962","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/76/882"},"text":"76 Stat. 882","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"id788d65ba-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1980—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/470"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–470","children":[],"tail":" struck out subsec. (a) which required Secretary of the Interior to make an annual report to Congress with respect to activities of United States Fish and Wildlife Service under this Act, accompanied by appropriate legislative recommendations."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1975—Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/93/618"},"text":"Pub. L. 93–618","children":[],"tail":" substituted “United States International Trade Commission” for “United States Tariff Commission”."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"execDoc","id":"id788d65bb-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Executive Documents","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"transferOfFunctions","id":"id788d65bc-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Transfer of Functions","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Transfer of functions to Secretary of Commerce from Secretary of the Interior by Reorg. Plan No. 4 of 1970, eff. ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1970-10-03"},"text":"Oct. 3, 1970","children":[],"tail":", 35 F.R. 15627, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/84/2090"},"text":"84 Stat. 2090","children":[],"tail":", see note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s742b"},"text":"section 742b of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
